All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    APoint
    Mathematical method creating a point of coordinates x and y
    ButtonHandler
    Classe enabling to play the sounds on button press
    Enemy
    Creation of the aliens in this class, with their texture and conditions on their death
    Game
    Main class calling the Welcome Window to start a game
    GamePanel
    Main Panel calling every elements (SlingShot, Projectile, Aliens and Blocks) Display them and compute the launch of the projectile
    GameWindow
    Main Window containing all the games It contains GamePanel and the Game Loop
    LevelsWindow
    Selection Level Window, basic display to select between 3 levels
    Material
    Creation of the blocks in this class, with their texture and conditions on their destruction As well as future method for force computations
    Music
    Music class creating all the necessary stuff such as the AudioInput, File And enables the play, loop, stop actions for the music
    Object
    Mother class of Materials, Aliens and Projectile Most of attributes are declared here and contains the code for the gravityAction and Collision Detection
    Projectile
    Method computing every characteristic of the projectile (Speed, Position, Display)
    SoundEffect
    Class creating the Sound effects such as click ones Using the same principle as Music
    Terrain
    Class containing the world where the game is played, filled with the background image and the elements aliens and blocks
    Terrain2
    Inherit from the first class Terrain to create the world and changes some parameters Such as gravity, aliens, blocks etc.
    Terrain3
    Inherit from the first class Terrain to create the world and changes some parameters Such as gravity, aliens, blocks etc.
    Thrower
    Class of the slingshot containing its computation methods and display
    TransitionWindow
    Window appearing when the player won the game, gives the possibility to replay or continue to the next level
    WelcomeWindow
    it's the welcoming window as indicated, where you enter the name and can choose to play directly or go to the selection window
